text = "Accessibility is a priority in the development of this game. It should be usable with mouse or keyboard, and by users who are Deaf, colorblind, low vision, or blind and using a screenreader. There is no time pressure or flashing lights.

On the Options page, you can chose which six dangers will come up on the dice. If spiders are a deal breaker for you, how about a wolf or a chainsaw instead?

If you find this game particularly accessible, or if something doesn't work for you, please let us know on the itch.io page."
